@startuml startup
title RAMA Startup Sequence

start

:Detect PR event (pull_request opened/reopened/synchronize);
:Trigger GitHub Actions workflow;
:Checkout PR head (source) revision;
:Build and execute RAMA;
:Look for `rama.json` configuration file;

if (Is `rama.json` missing/empty/invalid?) then (yes)
  :Display warning about configuration;
  :Use default configuration;
else (no)
  :Parse configuration;
  :Set model/metamodel extensions 
   and metamodel resolution rules;
endif

:Fetch PR file list and changed paths from GitHub API;
:Analyze each affected file → <pr-model-file-cases-all.puml>;

stop
@enduml
